import { library} from "@fortawesome/fontawesome-svg-core";

import {faHome, faTrashAlt, faChartArea, faBrain, faBorderNone, faPuzzlePiece, faQuestion, faInfo,
    faUserShield, faSignInAlt, faQuestionCircle, faCheckCircle, faFileAudio, faMicrophoneAlt,
    faMicrophoneAltSlash, faChevronLeft, faChevronRight, faTools} from "@fortawesome/free-solid-svg-icons";

library.add(
    faTools,
    faChevronLeft,
    faChevronRight,
    faMicrophoneAltSlash,
    faMicrophoneAlt,
    faFileAudio,
    faCheckCircle,
    faHome,
    faTrashAlt,
    faChartArea,
    faBrain,
    faBorderNone,
    faPuzzlePiece,
    faQuestion,
    faInfo,
    faUserShield,
    faSignInAlt,
    faQuestionCircle
);
